latestIgtvVideos.title: RAKHI OUTFIT INSPO🥻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It is always great to wear fusion clothes, which doesn't makes you look basic and mainstream. 
And on festival like Rakhi, we don't really go full traditional or western and that is why it is always satisfying to mix and match clothes. 
I hope you liked the idea and please do lemme know in comment section.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Uncomfortable wearing a bikini or a bikini top?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The most important rule when wearing any outfit is to wear it with confidence. If a skimpy bikini isn’t for you, then take a look at these styles where you can wear a bikini top with a knot shirt (which usually everyone has) so that it covers a little more and yet it makes you look sexy. 
Beach outfit with shorts are also a good option, you can ring the changes by changing your choice of top. A pair of little shorts works perfectly with a bikini top and on top of that classic blue denim never loses its appeal and gives the coolest of beach looks. 
Provided, you can also try wearing these styles as a daywear with a pair of jeans or something full so that it doesn’t overdo.
